params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetParent_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetParent_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetParent_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetParent_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_MANHOUR_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" as \\"Det_PS_EDITION\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') || '/' || to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_UNIT_QTY\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Det_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Det_EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Det_EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_SPOIL\\", " +" M_PS.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"Det_CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_LT_FLG\\" as \\"Det_PS_LT_FLG\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_FIXED_LT\\") as \\"Det_PS_FIXED_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LT\\") as \\"Det_PS_PROP_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Det_PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_REF_NO\\") as \\"Det_PS_REF_NO\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COST_UP_TYP\\" as \\"Det_COST_UP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" as \\"Det_MRP_EXP_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Parent, " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Comp, " +" M_PS M_PS " +"where " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"DetComp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MRP_ODR_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_MRP_ODR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" as \\"DetComp_OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"MANHOUR_TYP\\" as \\"Det_MANHOUR_TYP\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"DETCOMP_STOCK_UNIT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"Sub1Parent_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"Sub1Comp_ITEM_NAME\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Sub1_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" M_ITEM_Comp.\\"STOCK_UNIT\\" as \\"Sub1Comp_STOCK_UNIT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Sub1_EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"Sub1_EFF_PHASE_OUT_DATE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_SPOIL\\", 'FM99990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_SPOIL\\", " +" M_PS.\\"CONS_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_CONS_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"PS_LT_FLG\\" as \\"Sub1_PS_LT_FLG\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_FIXED_LT\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_FIXED_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LT\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_PROP_LT\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", 'FM99999999999990.0999') as \\"Sub1_PS_PROP_LOT_SIZE\\", " +" to_char(M_PS.\\"PS_REF_NO\\") as \\"Sub1_PS_REF_NO\\", " +" M_PS.\\"COST_UP_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_COST_UP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MRP_EXP_TYP\\" as \\"Sub1_MRP_EXP_TYP\\", " +" M_PS.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"h_Sub1_MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Parent, " +" M_ITEM M_ITEM_Comp, " +" M_PS M_PS " +"where " +" M_ITEM_Parent.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_ITEM_Comp.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PS.\\"PARENT_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"COMP_ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PS.\\"PS_EDITION\\" = ?"
